  <brief_title>Therapy of Acute Myeloid Leukemia in Patients Over the Age of 60 : DA Versus Mitoxantrone With Intermittent AraC</brief_title>
  <official_title>Therapy of AML in Patients Older Than 60 Years: Randomized Comparison of a Double Induction With Daunorubicin and AraC (as Continuous Infusion) With a Double Induction With Mitoxantrone and Intermittent, Medium High Dose AraC</official_title>
