  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of AML

          -  age &gt;60

          -  no previous Chemo for AML

          -  informed consent

          -  Karnofsky &gt;70

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  AML M3

          -  uncontrolled Sepsis

          -  uncontrolled HYpertension

          -  respiratory failure

          -  heart-failure NYHA IV, recent myocardial infarction

          -  severe organ dysfunction of liver, kidneys,

          -  HIV -infection or active Hepatitis B,C
      </textblock>
